snippet.title: [ArcheWorld] Development Sneak Peek: Progression system and the Exchange
snippet.description:
Hello, Archeans! We are glad to show you another in-game footage about ‘Progression System and the Exchange’. In this SneakPeek, you can see the progression of pets and gears, as well as the trade of Archeum in the Exchange. I hope you enjoy the video and please look forward to more Sneak Peeks in the following weeks! Thank you.

*The video was taken in a development stage,
and some changes may occur. #아키월드 #ArcheWorld #nft #nftgame #nftgames #playandearn #PanduanArcheWorld #ArcheWorld指南 #คำแนะนำArcheWorld #nftcommunity #nftgaming #Archeworldingame #블록체인 #암호화폐
